Estimated resource needs for Claude (Cowork mode):
The Claude desktop app runs a lightweight Linux VM in the background, so on top of the app itself, you'd want to account for:

RAM: Reserve around 2–4 GB for the app and its VM. If you're running other heavy applications simultaneously, having 8 GB total system RAM or more is advisable.
CPU: No dedicated CPU reservation is strictly required, but a modern dual-core processor or better ensures smooth operation. The VM spins up on demand so CPU usage is intermittent rather than constant.
Disk: A few GB of free disk space for the VM environment and any temporary files.

